[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":461},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fgit\u002F20220724\u002F3916507104\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fgit\u002F20220724\u002F3916507104\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fgit\u002F20220724\u002F3916507104\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fgit\u002F20220724\u002F3916507104\u002F":438,"related:\u002Fgit\u002F20220724\u002F3916507104\u002F":447},"\u002Fen\u002Fgit\u002F2022\u002F07\u002F24\u002Fwhat-is-ds-store-should-you-commit-it\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":421,"date":422,"description":423,"extension":424,"lang":425,"meta":426,"navigation":182,"path":427,"readingMinutes":428,"seo":429,"standalone":430,"stem":431,"tags":432,"tldr":434,"updated":435,"url":436,"__hash__":437},"content\u002FGit\u002F靠北-DS-Store-到底是什麼？該不該加入到版本控制內？.md","靠北 .DS_Store 到底是什麼？該不該加入到版本控制內？","3916507104",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":413},"minimark",[11,31,35,38,42,45,52,55,77,84,91,104,110,113,117,120,123,273,276,280,283,308,311,314,331,334,337,375,378,382,385,388,391,394,397,409],[12,13,14],"blockquote",{},[15,16,17,21,22,26,27,30],"p",{},[18,19,20],"strong",{},"Note","\n.DS_Store 是 macOS 在每個資料夾下自動產生的隱藏檔，會儲存資料夾的圖示、視窗位置等顯示設定。Finder 不會顯示它，要看到只能開終端機輸入 ",[23,24,25],"code",{},"ls -la","。",[18,28,29],{},"不建議","加入 Git 版控，多數框架的 .gitignore 預設都會忽略它。",[32,33,34],"h2",{"id":34},"前言",[15,36,37],{},".DS_Store 到底是什麼東西？它到底該不該加入到版本控制內？為什麼會有它呢？所以這一篇就簡單聊一下 .DS_Store 這個東西。",[32,39,41],{"id":40},"ds_store-是什麼",".DS_Store 是什麼？",[15,43,44],{},".DS_Store 是 MacOS 作業系統專屬的隱藏文件，英文全稱為「Desktop Services Store」，如果你是 Microsoft Windows 開發者的話，你可以把它想像成是 desktop.ini，但這一篇主要是說明 .DS_Store 是什麼，因此 Microsoft Windows 就可以離開啦~",[15,46,47,48,51],{},"那麼由於 .DS_Store 本身是一個隱藏資料夾，那麼查看隱藏資料夾的方式是在 Finder 視窗按下組合按鈕 ",[23,49,50],{},"Command + Shift + ."," 即可以顯示(反之再按一次就會隱藏)，但就算你這樣做你也會發現根本沒有辦法看到 .DS_Store。",[15,53,54],{},"因為 Finder 並不會直接顯示出 .DS_Store，而是你必須使用終端機並輸入以下指令才能看到",[56,57,62],"pre",{"className":58,"code":59,"language":60,"meta":61,"style":61},"language-sh shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","ls -la\n","sh","",[23,63,64],{"__ignoreMap":61},[65,66,69,73],"span",{"class":67,"line":68},"line",1,[65,70,72],{"class":71},"s_sBn","ls",[65,74,76],{"class":75},"sCcAr"," -la\n",[15,78,79],{},[80,81],"img",{"alt":82,"src":83},".DS_Store","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fvun6IFu.png",[15,85,86,87,90],{},"除此之外你也可以輸入 ",[23,88,89],{},"file"," 來查看 .DS_Store 是什麼類型的檔案",[56,92,94],{"className":58,"code":93,"language":60,"meta":61,"style":61},"file .DS_Store\n",[23,95,96],{"__ignoreMap":61},[65,97,98,100],{"class":67,"line":68},[65,99,89],{"class":71},[65,101,103],{"class":102},"sTRMh"," .DS_Store\n",[15,105,106],{},[80,107],{"alt":108,"src":109},"Desktop Services Store","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FSDYDwfE.png",[15,111,112],{},"那 .DS_Store 到底是什麼呢？簡單來講 .DS_Store 裡面主要儲存了一些資訊，例如：資料夾的圖標、視窗的設置等等，因此通常 .DS_Store 在每一個資料夾內都有，基本上就是隨處可見的等級了，但 .DS_Store 並不會佔用太多記憶體空間，所以通常來講是不用去特別理會它。",[32,114,116],{"id":115},"該不該把-ds_store-加入版本控制","該不該把 .DS_Store 加入版本控制",[15,118,119],{},"其實這個答案非常淺顯易見，就是「不建議」加入版本控制內，就如同前面所言， .DS_Store 會記錄一些資訊，因此如果將 .DS_Store 加入到版本控制內時，是有可能發生一些資訊安全的問題(僅僅是有可能而已)。",[15,121,122],{},"因此許多 CLI 預設的 .gitignore 都會忽略 .DS_Store，以下舉例 Vite 的 .gitignore",[56,124,128],{"className":125,"code":126,"language":127,"meta":61,"style":61},"language-.gitignore shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","# Logs\nlogs\n*.log\nnpm-debug.log*\nyarn-debug.log*\nyarn-error.log*\npnpm-debug.log*\nlerna-debug.log*\n\nnode_modules\ndist\ndist-ssr\n*.local\n\n# Editor directories and files\n.vscode\u002F*\n!.vscode\u002Fextensions.json\n.idea\n.DS_Store\n*.suo\n*.ntvs*\n*.njsproj\n*.sln\n*.sw?\n",".gitignore",[23,129,130,135,141,147,153,159,165,171,177,184,190,196,202,208,213,219,225,231,237,243,249,255,261,267],{"__ignoreMap":61},[65,131,132],{"class":67,"line":68},[65,133,134],{},"# Logs\n",[65,136,138],{"class":67,"line":137},2,[65,139,140],{},"logs\n",[65,142,144],{"class":67,"line":143},3,[65,145,146],{},"*.log\n",[65,148,150],{"class":67,"line":149},4,[65,151,152],{},"npm-debug.log*\n",[65,154,156],{"class":67,"line":155},5,[65,157,158],{},"yarn-debug.log*\n",[65,160,162],{"class":67,"line":161},6,[65,163,164],{},"yarn-error.log*\n",[65,166,168],{"class":67,"line":167},7,[65,169,170],{},"pnpm-debug.log*\n",[65,172,174],{"class":67,"line":173},8,[65,175,176],{},"lerna-debug.log*\n",[65,178,180],{"class":67,"line":179},9,[65,181,183],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":182},true,"\n",[65,185,187],{"class":67,"line":186},10,[65,188,189],{},"node_modules\n",[65,191,193],{"class":67,"line":192},11,[65,194,195],{},"dist\n",[65,197,199],{"class":67,"line":198},12,[65,200,201],{},"dist-ssr\n",[65,203,205],{"class":67,"line":204},13,[65,206,207],{},"*.local\n",[65,209,211],{"class":67,"line":210},14,[65,212,183],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":182},[65,214,216],{"class":67,"line":215},15,[65,217,218],{},"# Editor directories and files\n",[65,220,222],{"class":67,"line":221},16,[65,223,224],{},".vscode\u002F*\n",[65,226,228],{"class":67,"line":227},17,[65,229,230],{},"!.vscode\u002Fextensions.json\n",[65,232,234],{"class":67,"line":233},18,[65,235,236],{},".idea\n",[65,238,240],{"class":67,"line":239},19,[65,241,242],{},".DS_Store\n",[65,244,246],{"class":67,"line":245},20,[65,247,248],{},"*.suo\n",[65,250,252],{"class":67,"line":251},21,[65,253,254],{},"*.ntvs*\n",[65,256,258],{"class":67,"line":257},22,[65,259,260],{},"*.njsproj\n",[65,262,264],{"class":67,"line":263},23,[65,265,266],{},"*.sln\n",[65,268,270],{"class":67,"line":269},24,[65,271,272],{},"*.sw?\n",[15,274,275],{},"但為了保護開發者，還是會建議 .gitignore 要將 .DS_Store 加入忽略清單內。",[32,277,279],{"id":278},"阻止-ds_store-的生成","阻止 .DS_Store 的生成",[15,281,282],{},"當然也可以阻止 .DS_Store 的生成，只需要在終端機輸入以下指令",[56,284,286],{"className":58,"code":285,"language":60,"meta":61,"style":61},"defaults write com.apple.desktopservices DSDontWriteNetworkStores -bool TRUE\n",[23,287,288],{"__ignoreMap":61},[65,289,290,293,296,299,302,305],{"class":67,"line":68},[65,291,292],{"class":71},"defaults",[65,294,295],{"class":102}," write",[65,297,298],{"class":102}," com.apple.desktopservices",[65,300,301],{"class":102}," DSDontWriteNetworkStores",[65,303,304],{"class":75}," -bool",[65,306,307],{"class":102}," TRUE\n",[15,309,310],{},"接下來重新啟動 Mac 就可以了。",[15,312,313],{},"若你想要恢復生成 .DS_Store，可以使用以下指令",[56,315,317],{"className":58,"code":316,"language":60,"meta":61,"style":61},"defaults delete com.apple.desktopservices DSDontWriteNetworkStores\n",[23,318,319],{"__ignoreMap":61},[65,320,321,323,326,328],{"class":67,"line":68},[65,322,292],{"class":71},[65,324,325],{"class":102}," delete",[65,327,298],{"class":102},[65,329,330],{"class":102}," DSDontWriteNetworkStores\n",[15,332,333],{},"同上，恢復生成後要記得重新啟動 Mac",[15,335,336],{},"如果是想要搜尋 + 刪除當前 Mac 裡面所有 .DS_Store 檔案，可以使用以下指令",[56,338,340],{"className":58,"code":339,"language":60,"meta":61,"style":61},"sudo find . -name \".DS_Store\" -depth -exec rm {} \\;  \n",[23,341,342],{"__ignoreMap":61},[65,343,344,347,350,353,356,359,362,365,368,371],{"class":67,"line":68},[65,345,346],{"class":71},"sudo",[65,348,349],{"class":102}," find",[65,351,352],{"class":102}," .",[65,354,355],{"class":75}," -name",[65,357,358],{"class":102}," \".DS_Store\"",[65,360,361],{"class":75}," -depth",[65,363,364],{"class":75}," -exec",[65,366,367],{"class":102}," rm",[65,369,370],{"class":102}," {}",[65,372,374],{"class":373},"sWyjQ"," \\;\n",[15,376,377],{},"基本上這樣子就不會一直長出 .DS_Store 了。",[32,379,381],{"id":380},"ds_store-該不該刪除或停用",".DS_Store 該不該刪除或停用？",[15,383,384],{},"其實認真來講是不建議刪除或停用，儘管你是可以這樣做，也沒有任何問題。",[15,386,387],{},"但是除非你有什麼特別的原因，不然 .DS_Store 是不會影響你的效能的，通常也不會有太多的資安問題，除此之外 .DS_Store 主要也是幫你記錄一些資訊，如果你刪除的話可能會出現一些問題。",[15,389,390],{},"所以這個問題就留給你自己思考。",[15,392,393],{},"但有一點可以很明確的告知為了保護開發者，還是會建議 .gitignore 要將 .DS_Store 加入忽略清單內。",[32,395,396],{"id":396},"參考文獻",[398,399,400],"ul",{},[401,402,403],"li",{},[404,405,82],"a",{"href":406,"rel":407},"https:\u002F\u002Fzh.wikipedia.org\u002Fzh-tw\u002F.DS_Store",[408],"nofollow",[410,411,412],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}",{"title":61,"searchDepth":137,"depth":137,"links":414},[415,416,417,418,419,420],{"id":34,"depth":137,"text":34},{"id":40,"depth":137,"text":41},{"id":115,"depth":137,"text":116},{"id":278,"depth":137,"text":279},{"id":380,"depth":137,"text":381},{"id":396,"depth":137,"text":396},"Git","2022-07-24 14:21:17",".DS_Store 到底是什麼？為什麼 macOS 每個資料夾都會偷偷生一個？該不該 commit 到 Git？這一篇從它的由來說起，告訴你為什麼最好直接加進 .gitignore。","md","zh-Hant",{},"\u002Fgit\u002Fds-store","2",{"title":6,"description":423},false,"Git\u002F靠北-DS-Store-到底是什麼？該不該加入到版本控制內？",[82,421,127,433],"macOS",null,"2026-05-12 09:00:00","\u002Fgit\u002F20220724\u002F3916507104\u002F","vi9nSlm59b-Fy6JzCc_3wqHWm7OZQsAMhAMC0YFfmIQ",{"newer":439,"older":443},{"url":440,"title":441,"date":442},"\u002Fother\u002F20220823\u002F3996969975\u002F","Discord 外掛 - 用 BetterDiscord 強化你的 Discord","2022-08-23 15:04:18",{"url":444,"title":445,"date":446},"\u002Fvscode\u002F20220712\u002F2790345819\u002F","VSCode 1.69 !+tab 無效問題(更新)","2022-07-12 09:55:45",[448,453,457],{"url":449,"title":450,"date":451,"readingMinutes":452},"\u002Fgit\u002F20260226\u002F799954596\u002F","取代 git push --force 更好的方式，git push --force-with-lease","2026-02-26 09:39:40","4",{"url":454,"title":455,"date":456,"readingMinutes":428},"\u002Fgit\u002F20260122\u002F21277993\u002F","Git init 出現 master 分支提示？教你設定預設分支為 main","2026-01-22 16:20:40",{"url":458,"title":459,"date":460,"readingMinutes":452},"\u002Fgit\u002F20260121\u002F2025687513\u002F","Git Worktree 是什麼？一個專案同時跑多個 AI Agent 的秘訣","2026-01-21 16:04:27",1784013081356]